                            Rafikistry is a Teen Life Centre with Tender Loving Care, where we Trounce, Learn and Chillax!<br>
                            As the name suggests, Rafikistry TLC is all about Friendships!
                            ‘Rafiki’ is the Kiswahili word for ‘friend’. A friend is one who gives help and support.<br>

                            We exist to provide and increase information and skills on physical, mental, social, sexual and reproductive health as components of holistic wellbeing.<br>

                            For more than 10 years, Rafikistry has continued to provide services in a confidential and non-judgemental environment free from discrimination, coercion and violence.
